<br>
Lure AE Mobs = HP Gear<br>
<br>
Resistable AE Mobs = SV Gear<br>
<br>
Normal Mobs = Mana Gear<br>
<br>
<br>
More Mana = More Heals.<br>
<br>
More AC/HP = Less Mana<br>
<br>
Less Mana = Not so many Heals<br>
<br>
Not so many Heals = Grp Deeed<br>
<br>
Grp Deeeeed = @#%$ up Raid<br>
<br>
@#%$ up Raid = CR<br>
<br>
CR = Sucks<br>
