Unsurprisingly, I stress maxed mana then HPs; so I'm 2283 HPs and 3687 mana unbuffed;  What that is with Coat and Glades I'd have to log in and check.  :)<br>
<br>
Edit: With Glades and Coat: 2753 HP, and 1100ac on the dot - though the druid cap is significantly lower we think, one can never be certain. ;)<br>
<br>
<a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=37093">My usual gear</a><br>
<br>
I concentrated on reaching the mana cap first of all, and then started beefing up my HPs (so, using Barbed Dragon Boots for the 57hp instead of Leatherfoot Sandals, etc.).  Rather than holding out for Rowyl's Armguards (no HP, but nice resists), I went for Ssra's Eyepatch (10 less resists, but +75hp and Truesight), and am currently looking for ways of swapping out mana for HP in order to get back under the mana cap with GoB - I'm taking suggestions (working on the 3rd Chardok quest)! :)<br>
<br>
All good fun!<br>
<br>
